{"word":"προσικνέομαι","slug":"προσικνέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσικνέομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ίξομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to come to, reach</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to reach so far as, come at</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; also, <el>πρ. ἐφ' ἧπαρ</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to approach as a suppliant</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> loci, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}